title: Orbx FTX US PAGS Gustavus
description:
The charming little Gustavus Airport is the latest from Russ White, who continues to explore the Alaskan wilderness.
With its great runway facility, open terrain and easy approach, the Gustavus Airfield is a perfect gateway to the Icy Strait area and is used heavily in the summer months when thousands of visitors from the world over visit.
